data.description: Like NEW Bridge City home, ready for its new owner! New siding, several new windows, new exterior paint, lots of updates! 3 bedrooms, and a large game room/sunroom. In-door laundry space, two living areas, and an outdoor 2nd floor deck! Very unique layout with main living upstairs including kitchen and primary bedroom, both floors have a breaker that can be switched off/on and still operate one or the other. In case of a bad storm, you can easily live on the second floor and completely shut off the first floor. This home has never flooded and the lot is super high! Storage building will be removed along with chicken coop and chickens. Two drive ways, shade trees, and located at the end of a dead end street! Come enjoy the view, this home was built 2019! Call for your showing!
